history.text: I haven't seen this movie, but my daughter liked it.
What movie is it ?  I haven't seen many movies in the theaters lately.
My daughter likes to keep seeing it on TV
What network is it on ?  I see Harry Potter played often on repeat.
It's been a long time since it was in the theatres
I think it comes on Disney and some other channels
I think she has some Frozen toys
I've only seen parts of the movie frozen, but you couldn't really miss the merchandising.
Will there be a sequel to Frozen?
Yeah, all things are merchandized these days.
I think there will be a sequal to frozen, but I haven't seen that movie.  The movie Ice Age is like frozen
And there are many Ice Age sequels.
I think I've heard of that, but don't know much about it.
So was the movie you were thinking Ice Age or something else ?
Really? How many Ice Age movies have there been?
It's a bit hard to say. I don't think I know very much about Ice Age movies.
I think there were at least 4 with the one that is about to come out, they all have varying names.
Maybe it was a movie with a disney princess
Wow. I didn't know that.
Do you like these movies?
Not really !  I like Harry Potter over those movies.
I think my daughter has seen a few movies like that, but I don't really watch them.
A Wrinkle In Time seems like a good movie that will be coming out soon.  A fantasy story.  Was the movie you were thinking about a sci fi fantasy?
I have only seen parts of a couple of Harry Potter movies.
Not sure. But I have seen previews of A Wrinkle In Time. Looks like it might be ineteresting.
Do you know the lead actor in the movie you were thinking about ?  There are a lot of female leads lately.
I mostly like Action/Adventure movies. Sometimes dramas. I like comdeies, but most of them are dumb.
I don't keep much track of actors lately.
Was the movie animated or a regular movie, that your daughter liked ?
Movies are expensive to go to these days.
Very expensive.  And it's so easy to stream whatever you want from home.
I don't think I've gone to a theatre in 18 months.
Yes you can stream very easily.
Moana is another movie that was really popular, a disney movie I believe.
Except I don't think it's on tv yet, but maybe.

uid2response.feedback: I tried to have the user tell me the name of the movie, but they would not share that information.  They said that their daughter liked the movie and maybe it was on television, and also a disney movie.   I did ask many leading questions but was not successful.  Also, I was not given a document to read.
